<p><strong>E:</strong> a catalog of products like <a href="https://www.festo.com/cat/en-us_us/products">this?</a></p>

<p><strong>P:</strong> several other companies that can generate and serve web catalogs [2]</p>

<p><strong>E:</strong> ‚ÄúMarketplace MCI (www.internetmci.com)</p>

