$2000/mo‚Äù</p>

<p><strong>P:</strong> difficult</p>

<p><strong>E:</strong> No idea</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>So the next best solution is to have a (general-purpose catalog
generator)[1], but have someone else handle the server
